com.knowgate.crm

Class CompanyLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.knowgate.crm.CompanyLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImportLoader

    public final class CompanyLoader
extends java.lang.Object
implements ImportLoader

    Load Company and Address data from a single source

    Company loader creates or updates simultaneously registers at k_companies and k_addresses tables and the links between them k_x_contact_addr. Loading a Company is a special case of loading a contact, and thus this class delegates all its behavious to a private ContactLoader member.
    Version:
    4.0
